                                  User Stories

1. As a priest I want to be able to change the order of the songs for each service.
2. As a priest I want to be able to print the schedule for songs that will be sung this service, in order.
2. As a church goer I want to be able to see the current song that is been sung at the service.
3. As a church goer I want to be able to access the options menu.
4. As A church goer I want to be able to donate to the church through paypal at the push of button.
5. As A member of the church I want to be able to connect to a external device to get today readings.
